{"tid":543056,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"禾絲妮雅琪：「我肯定利物浦終有一天會英超冠軍。」","createTime":"2018-01-28T06:08:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T10:16:57.000Z","uid":133756,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5fca7464860dcfaf49633237d5aa9b5d9b85ad25","tid":543056,"uid":133756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T06:08:02.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=xl%2FLXOVrUJasthmZibJTJ2xr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=cfda3497\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】周六誕生的澳洲網球公開賽女單冠軍得主禾絲妮雅琪，賽後以自己的例子勉勵利物浦，繼續向第1次贏取英超冠軍的夢想進發。<br />\n<br />\n禾絲妮雅琪（Caroline Wozniacki）是利物浦的粉絲，也是公開的秘密，她更曾穿著紅軍8號隊長謝拉特的波衫打網球。周六女單賽後被問到利物浦的英超夢，「丹麥甜心」先以廣告口吻說：「無事沒可能。」她亦公開為利物浦打氣：「我可肯定，他們終有一天完成目標。」<br />\n<br />\n禾琪追逐多年的大滿貫冠軍夢，終在周六的澳洲公開賽女單決賽完成，並當上歷來第1位贏取大滿貫冠軍的丹麥人。禾絲妮雅琪此前曾於2次美國公開賽女單決賽飲恨，周六揚威墨爾本可謂遲來的吐氣揚眉。<br />\n<br />\n禾琪的激勵，相信令剛在足總盃被踢出局的紅軍，或多或少受到激勵。早前曾以4:3勇挫英超一哥曼城的利物浦，現時落後藍月亮18分，暫列英超榜第4位。"},{"pid":"bb82d96a0c9516a1afa92e44c8da043bce588a0c","tid":543056,"uid":36049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T06:13:56.000Z","msg":"公開抽猁,屌牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d48dc50a44bebaf9b9c7d594a3ed1d424999e7","tid":543056,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T06:16:28.000Z","msg":"好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連女人都睇利記唔起"},{"pid":"9cb6d318dd456bc3f9be1a7c0e878146c5ad1fea","tid":543056,"uid":54524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T06:17:12.000Z","msg":"終有一天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c0fd5d79b8cf3d7902ea463fc07d994c88baf2